{"tid":899070,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"會計妹變虛疑 YouTuber　兩個月觀看次數達 400 萬","createTime":"2018-11-12T06:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T10:50:09.000Z","uid":51464,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8e7bd8276025e3cf4720596f2dbd9f2db8155ef5","tid":899070,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T06:42:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2205031\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2205031&d=wHrsVXbTJXHmsiuUBrJSVACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=1c43aa1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2205031</a><br />\n<br />\n近年日本 YouTube 興起 Virtual YouTuber 熱潮，主播會以 3D 虛擬角色取代自己的形像，再以自己的聲線或電腦聲線為 Virtual YouTuber 配音製作影片。會計妹可算是香港最早出現的虛擬偶像之一，該角色除了為旗下公司宣傳外，最近會計妹更向 Virtual YouTuber 的路線出發，而且在短短兩個月內影片觀看次數達 400 萬次，觀看次數比起本港不少真人 YouTuber 還要高。<br />\n=====<br />\nIn 會計妹 I trust!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f99fc88cb0deedc6ffa35ff59362b2859a3e3f","tid":899070,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T06:47:01.000Z","msg":"=.="},{"pid":"14865a1b2de6c725981fdd56fbc90455d714ef57","tid":899070,"uid":34409,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T06:48:00.000Z","msg":"日本代表~~輝夜月<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TeKTVFgw1hM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTeKTVFgw1hM&d=wHrsVXb